Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.94,0:00:07.48,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1048,310)\c&HFD48D2&}這是、夏天的回憶。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.65,0:00:29.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.40,0:00:35.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.20,0:00:38.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,響？太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個人到處亂跑可不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.33,0:00:43.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.79,0:00:46.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你把響帶回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.67,0:00:48.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.13,0:00:52.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用向我道謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.22,0:00:54.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.37,0:02:32.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家能一起來遊樂園 好令人興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.54,0:02:32.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.84,0:02:38.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上同學 難道說不喜歡遊樂園麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.05,0:02:41.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 沒這回事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.43,0:02:44.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 畢竟這裡有鬼屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.01,0:02:48.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明都和天海相處了這麼久了還怕假的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.85,0:02:49.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吵死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.85,0:02:54.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇~遊樂園~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂 你還真是情緒高漲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.82,0:02:58.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看起來好好玩！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.32,0:03:02.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,噓！別和他對視！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.24,0:03:08.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 這個入場卷是天海給的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.04,0:03:13.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 是父親工作的同事給的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.83,0:03:15.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,據說是充滿回憶的遊樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.25,0:03:15.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}（啊 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}你好你好你好）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煩死了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.09,0:03:21.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這身打扮是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.13,0:03:22.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼你這傢伙會在這裡！山田的大哥！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.09,0:03:25.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呀~因為我很閒就參加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本就沒請你吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.22,0:03:29.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是我家大哥的厲害之處啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我沒誇他！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.69,0:03:32.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.40,0:03:34.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.73,0:03:36.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼像笨蛋一樣穿得一點都不清涼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在一本正經地胡說八道些什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.32,0:03:40.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在可是夏天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是女子高中生哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.24,0:03:45.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不趁著年輕的時候多做些不可以的事的話. . .
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.95,0:03:46.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她想做些不可以做的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.58,0:03:54.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算了吧算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們一起好好地去逛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.79,0:03:58.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘁 那好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在也不是搭理這種傢伙的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.63,0:04:05.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們這邊倒是也叫來了特別嘉賓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.01,0:04:07.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.06,0:04:08.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看這個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.06,0:04:12.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個我是同意了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.64,0:04:14.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地縛靈先生？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.98,0:04:18.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 雖然只有聲音和畫面啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有機會難得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們拜託了代答武士和小太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.49,0:04:27.24,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(584,532)}給代答武士 小太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.49,0:04:27.24,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1418,198)}我們大家要去遊樂場玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.49,0:04:27.24,S1,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(1436,328)}麻煩跟其他的幽靈說一聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.90,0:04:25.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以我覺得應該來了不少吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.12,0:04:26.62,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.45,0:04:30.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.25,0:04:33.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.42,0:04:36.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼沒有告訴我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果告訴你了 以你的性子一定會費很多心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管是對人還是對幽靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.26,0:04:44.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是個小小的驚喜啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被嚇得不輕的傢伙也是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事的哦 都是熟悉的幽靈們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.72,0:04:52.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是這個問題！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.65,0:04:58.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,全白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.86,0:05:03.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,儘管說是讓我吉田良生一個人待著 因為距離截稿只有三天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但完全沒有進展
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.99,0:05:09.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,面對就像在無限地擴展的空白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,反射過來的陽光讓人目眩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夏天了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.67,0:05:25.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,遊樂園這地方真 是 是個很奇妙的地方是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.47,0:05:28.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼哼 怎麼 你害怕了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.97,0:05:31.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才 才沒這回事是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.43,0:05:34.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係的哦 這裡是很有趣的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代答武士明顯害怕了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.60,0:05:40.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是說明明是個幽靈還怕鬼屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南蠻的騎馬武士來了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怕的是那個啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真蠢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.78,0:05:51.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個只是個機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.66,0:05:54.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以才說你們這些跟不上時代的武士啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.04,0:05:57.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的這東西都是這個樣子的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快點 放錢進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.17,0:06:02.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.59,0:06:04.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連這種事都能做到啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好有趣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再來一張再來一張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,靈異照片量產中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.14,0:06:14.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼啊 你不也是挺過時的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 你擋著了 礙事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.60,0:06:21.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我們去坐那個吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.69,0:06:26.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 這裡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.74,0:06:28.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不說也沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.03,0:06:30.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原來如此 有幽靈坐在那裡的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.28,0:06:32.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說過「別說」了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這麼說的話 這邊又怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.46,0:06:43.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 大家也要一起嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.26,0:06:50.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真奇怪 那個大姐姐在動之前就叫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.34,0:06:52.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,動了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真好玩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.23,0:07:00.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過有點暈昵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.73,0:07:06.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰來幫我解開一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:11.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.20,0:07:14.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裡有人穿裙子的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就能360度看到胖次了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.83,0:07:25.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.46,0:07:28.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是瑪麗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.76,0:07:34.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在正從360度注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.39,0:07:37.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要啊！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海殿下和地縛靈殿下一起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.27,0:07:47.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還要稍微朝下一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.82,0:07:48.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 這就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.49,0:07:51.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能很清楚地看到這裡的風景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.49,0:07:56.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過居然邀請幽靈來遊樂園玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.03,0:07:58.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你的朋友也是相當奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.50,0:08:01.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊 我嚇了一大跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你經常來這裡嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.38,0:08:09.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小時候好像有來過幾次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.34,0:08:12.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是都不大記得清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那傢伙好像也來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒？哪位啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為看起來很有趣 所以我就來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.78,0:08:33.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很歡迎！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.66,0:08:39.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧 終於輪到鬼屋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.83,0:08:42.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就讓我來確認一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上用紙巾準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.87,0:08:46.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,紙巾準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.63,0:08:47.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,護身符準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.04,0:08:49.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,護身符好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.38,0:08:50.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 入場！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來吧 會有什麼樣的鬼出現呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別嚇我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.72,0:09:03.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我們有這麼多人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺不是很害怕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 再加把勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an3}-比鬼怪還恐怖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,-我們中出了一個叛徒麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.45,0:09:20.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 你怕過頭了啦 井上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.70,0:09:21.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好想回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.58,0:09:27.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦 這個機關做得真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.96,0:09:29.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.42,0:09:34.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,每天都過著把脖子伸長去嚇唬人的生活…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海苔燒蛋？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,五個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,六個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.68,0:09:46.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,七個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.27,0:09:48.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,八個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,九個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.90,0:09:52.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,差了一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.53,0:09:59.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個 這個是吃便當用的不會碎的盤子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.49,0:10:00.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果不介意的話請收下！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.99,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,居然解決了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼要緊緊地黏在我後面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.54,0:10:08.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別在意別在意 難得來一次鬼屋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喵~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.63,0:10:13.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不覺得和你有點像嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.63,0:10:14.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不像啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,灼發的彌賽亞醬 那個那個那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才不像啊！混蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.44,0:10:34.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 這裡是鬼屋的最後了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.40,0:10:37.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是要說來這裡的路上被什麼嚇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.83,0:10:48.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是天海那傢伙完美的被冒牌貨嚇到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真盡興真盡興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.46,0:10:57.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說起來 天海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是說這裡有回憶什麼的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.13,0:11:01.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.47,0:11:04.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我記得不大清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.93,0:11:09.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小時候我在這裡迷路的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.40,0:11:12.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 迷路了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是恰好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.90,0:11:21.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好！那就由本大爺去叫工作人員過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.45,0:11:24.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就稍微和姐姐們玩一會兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.87,0:11:30.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是不是在哪兒見過？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.71,0:11:36.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 是的 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.67,0:11:39.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像找到了他的父母 我們就去匯合了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你能再來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.51,0:11:50.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個人迷路了的話會很害怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.06,0:11:51.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,孤零零的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.81,0:11:53.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.74,0:12:06.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.58,0:12:09.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下次再和朋友一起來玩哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.54,0:12:15.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以說你怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.43,0:12:27.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我再一次和朋友來玩了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熊貓君與你記錄美好瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,代返侍和小太妹請往裡靠靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.65,0:12:40.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家也稍微靠裡些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.11,0:12:43.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後因為把花子小姐擋住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小川請蹲下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.03,0:12:51.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好了 那拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.16,0:12:56.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熊…熊…我是熊貓君
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,熊貓君喝了個水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.67,0:13:00.13,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咔嚓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.76,0:13:05.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我回來了 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.55,0:13:06.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,歡迎回來 響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.97,0:13:07.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.51,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 歡迎大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.14,0:13:12.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,終於到了我們今天活動的重頭戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.85,0:13:14.81,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天海家留宿！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那個…你們兩位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.48,0:13:24.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用管我們 我們睡院子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們不能選擇打道回府麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.16,0:13:28.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼可以錯過炎炎夏日裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和活潑的女高中生一起同居的歡鬧機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.62,0:13:38.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.38,0:13:42.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打擾啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.38,0:13:43.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,留下來住是不錯啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過我們家真的可以麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.13,0:13:47.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,當然啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你沒關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡比鬼屋還恐怖的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先不說有沒有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.10,0:13:58.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之在朋友家留宿不是很正常的事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.52,0:14:00.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的你們太大驚小怪了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.15,0:14:09.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我們做點什麼好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咱們玩詞語接龍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.58,0:14:12.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不錯呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.99,0:14:14.66,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃 是麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.25,0:14:17.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 那從我開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.63,0:14:21.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竹筒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,MK5
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.09,0:14:23.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,武士道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.75,0:14:25.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翅膀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.84,0:14:26.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抽水馬桶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.09,0:14:28.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乞力馬扎囉！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.13,0:14:30.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,勞作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,夜深人靜秘密時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.39,0:14:36.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哇 比去遊樂園時候的數量還多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在苦思冥想這期間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.82,0:14:50.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世間高中生也在誆歌著令人感慨的青春麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.99,0:14:53.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家一起去遊樂園開心地玩耍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.33,0:14:56.04,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後去朋友家留宿麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.62,0:14:57.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,多麼令人羨慕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.58,0:15:01.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不對 我應該已經發誓要把靈魂獻給漫畫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.42,0:15:04.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了讓世人瞭解我漫畫的卓越之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論如何也要把夏天的大事件…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.63,0:15:10.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明年再動真格的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.14,0:15:14.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個…大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.18,0:15:17.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天晚飯吃什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.22,0:15:19.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 我幫你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.98,0:15:21.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.90,0:15:26.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 井上說要做奶奶特製的雞蛋燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.65,0:15:30.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別擅自做決定啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.78,0:15:35.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.03,0:15:37.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真沒想到竟然還能吃上女高中生親手做的飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.29,0:15:43.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感慨良多啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你趕快給我滾回院子去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.29,0:15:50.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,實際上今天的菜是小太妹的媽媽教我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誒 超好吃的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.59,0:15:55.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要說啦 也沒什麼太了不起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.39,0:15:57.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我很火大！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.51,0:15:59.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,井上的雞蛋燒也很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.60,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒 沒這回四似事啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.65,0:16:04.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完美地咬舌頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好啦 晚飯也吃完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.23,0:16:10.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下來就是夏天的經典活動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,來放煙花吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我帶浴衣來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.20,0:16:16.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.83,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為被要求帶過來了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姑且帶了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.66,0:16:24.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,女高中生穿浴衣的樣子麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍等 待我取下相機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.67,0:16:29.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用滾回院子你直給我滾回家去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這張是也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這邊啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.55,0:17:59.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傳說從睡在正中間的人的被子裡會鑽出幽靈來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.39,0:18:08.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要說這麼奇怪的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.23,0:18:12.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是的 我要睡了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.73,0:18:13.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.66,0:18:27.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在才想起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.96,0:18:30.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡到處都是幽靈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:36.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別嚇我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.18,0:18:42.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你睡不著嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不用管我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時候就睡著了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.88,0:19:22.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什…什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.43,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我爸爸曾對我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.39,0:19:33.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我小時候睡不著的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.35,0:19:35.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就這樣握住手心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.23,0:19:36.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.45,0:19:41.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更睡不著了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.95,0:19:43.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對…對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我太緊張了 手抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們在做什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.08,0:19:51.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,數個羊怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不要給你熱杯牛奶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.92,0:19:55.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.88,0:19:57.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都醒著嗎…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.67,0:19:59.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚睡一點也沒關係的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微幹點啥也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你抱著木刀睡的麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了防範那個蠢貨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.27,0:20:13.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那 就來唱催眠曲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.48,0:20:18.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要不乾脆就讓幽靈襲擊你 然後直接被嚇暈好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.53,0:20:20.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開玩笑啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都這個時候了 乾脆大家陪你一起熬夜好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.49,0:20:25.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒辦法呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽起來好像很有意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大家…謝謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.50,0:20:33.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天海道謝什麼的好奇怪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.83,0:20:34.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.12,0:20:36.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要道謝也該是這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.47,0:20:55.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼嘛 我們都已經做好熬夜的覺悟了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.11,0:20:58.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有點遺憾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.99,0:21:15.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,願從今往後也能如此和大家一起共度每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.75,0:22:00.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}對…對不起井上同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.84,0:22:03.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}我一直握到早上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.00,0:22:07.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}你這是啥情況 搞得我都害羞了啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.05,0:22:09.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,百合…大法好啊 哈哈哈哈哈

